  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Weapon Master's Handbook pg. 30</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 6th</p><p><strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can be placed only on melee weapons. The wielder of a <em>leveraging</em> weapon gains a bonus equal to the weapon's enhancement bonus to her Combat Maneuver Defense against bull rush, drag<sup>APG</sup>, reposition<sup>APG</sup>, and trip combat maneuvers. The <em>leveraging</em> weapon's enhancement bonus is doubled when applied to combat maneuver checks to attempt bull rush, drag, reposition, and trip combat maneuvers.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>enlarge person</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
